value.excerpt: A new book claims to shed light on former President Trump’s mindset in February of 2020 when his approval rating was surging and contains several quotes encapsulating the fierce contempt he held toward various Democratic presidential candidates.

value.excerpt: Former Presidentv Donald Trump easily won the 2024 GOP presidential nomination poll at the Conservative Political Action Conference (CPAC) gathering this weekend in Texas.

value.excerpt: Former President Donald Trump continued his fight against tech industry giants he claims are improperly censoring him, telling Fox News' "Sunday Morning Futures" that what Twitter, Facebook and YouTube are doing amounts to campaign contributions to Democrats.

value.title: Missouri AG Schmitt spotlights 'pushback' against Biden in 2022 Senate GOP primary
value.excerpt: In a crowded U.S. Senate GOP primary field, Missouri Attorney General Eric Schmitt says his efforts in taking on what he calls the "really radical" agenda of President Biden's administration is making his campaign stand out.

value.title: Pro-Biden super PAC warns voters can't name his accomplishments as midterms loom
value.excerpt: A super PAC supporting President Biden warns that Democrats could face defeat in the 2022 midterm elections if they don't campaign more "aggressively" on Biden's policies.

value.excerpt: Vice President Kamala Harris marveled at her full plate of major White House responsibilities quipping that she'll have to work on saying "no" to President Biden more often.

value.title: Trump-era DHS officials warn of ‘catastrophic’ results if Biden administration ends Title 42 border expulsions
value.excerpt: FIRST ON FOX: Former Homeland Security officials who served during the Trump administration are warning of dire consequences if the Biden administration ends a Trump-era public health rule that allows the rapid expulsion of migrants at the border due to the COVID-19 pandemic.

value.title: Budd: Trump endorsement ‘really accelerated’ GOP run for Senate in North Carolina
value.excerpt: Rep. Ted Budd says former President Trump’s endorsement of his 2022 campaign for Senate in North Carolina “really clarified things” in the battle for the Republican nomination.

value.title: West says Trump’s backing of Abbott ‘doesn’t hurt’ his primary challenge against Texas governor
value.excerpt: Outgoing Texas GOP chair Allen West insists that former President Trump’s endorsement of Gov. Greg Abbott “doesn’t hurt” his 2022 primary challenge against the two-term Republican governor.

value.excerpt: Donald Trump Jr. pledges he’ll be “everywhere” in the 2022 midterms, as the Republicans aim to win back the majorities in the House and Senate.

value.title: Biden fires Social Security Commissioner Andrew Saul, who says he isn't leaving
value.excerpt: President Biden fired Social Security Commissioner Andrew Saul on Friday amid an ongoing dispute over his leadership of the independent agency responsible for administering retirement and disability benefits.

value.title: Obama ethics chief blasts secret Hunter Biden art scheme arranged by White House
